Item.Name: Payment Entity
Item.Description: (Basic Data Source) provide data for the Payment.

DataSourceField.Name: Assigned Family Fee
DataSourceField.Description: The final saved value for family fee assigned for this payment.

DataSourceField.Name: Adjustment Comment
DataSourceField.Description: Comment entered when creating an Adjustment

DataSourceField.Name: Adjustment Reason Code
DataSourceField.Description: Reason entered when create an Adjustment.

DataSourceField.Name: Adjustment Sequence
DataSourceField.Description: Flag to record which Adjustment it is.

DataSourceField.Name: Adjustment Status Name
DataSourceField.Description: Only available when it is an Adjustment Payment

DataSourceField.Name: Amount（Don't Deduct Family Fee）
DataSourceField.Description: Total Amount without deduction of family fee.

DataSourceField.Name: Calculate User ID
DataSourceField.Description: ID of the user who commit this payment

DataSourceField.Name: Amount
DataSourceField.Description:
Adjustment = Final Total - Original Total
| Child Care = Final Total

DataSourceField.Name: Payment Status Code
DataSourceField.Description: Code of all payments status, including Denied, Voided

DataSourceField.Name: Payment Type
DataSourceField.Description: Field to distinct whether payment is Adjustment or not.

DataSourceField.Name: Is Digital
DataSourceField.Description: Whether it is a Digital Submission for this Payment. (True/False)

DataSourceField.Name: Payment End Date
DataSourceField.Description: The care End Date within this payment period.

DataSourceField.Name: Family Fee
DataSourceField.Description: The family fee value saved when first calculating the payment.

DataSourceField.Name: Has Adjustment
DataSourceField.Description: Whether this payment has any Adjustment? (True/False) When Adjustment is Denied, this field will be False. Any other Adjustment status will be True.

DataSourceField.Name: HasChange
DataSourceField.Description: Has Change in Payment related Care. (True/Fales)

DataSourceField.Name: Is License
DataSourceField.Description: Whether the Provider for this Payment is a License Provider. (True/False)

DataSourceField.Name: Is SDM
DataSourceField.Description: The flag to record whether the SDM is triggered.

DataSourceField.Name: Original Payment ID
DataSourceField.Description: The original Payment ID for Adjustment payment.

DataSourceField.Name: Total Other Amount
DataSourceField.Description: Sum of all Other Amount items

DataSourceField.Name: Payment Period End
DataSourceField.Description: End Date of the Payment period.

DataSourceField.Name: Payment Period Start
DataSourceField.Description: Start Date of the Payment period

DataSourceField.Name: Payment Start Date
DataSourceField.Description: The care Start Date within this payment period.

DataSourceField.Name: Payment Status Code
DataSourceField.Description: Code of all payments status, excluding Denied, Voided

DataSourceField.Name: Vendor ID
DataSourceField.Description: Vendor ID field in Provider Info
